        {
            "title": "鐵礦石價格對能源成本上升的敏感度有多高?",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/yztcdWicAvWjMjT_21H1Rg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/indicatornews_5_M_1440048359.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com – 瑞銀表示,<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"鐵礦石\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:鐵礦石;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/鐵礦石\">鐵礦石</a>價格對能源成本上升的敏感度正日益增強,因為油價上漲推高了全球礦業的運輸和生產成本。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">近期由中東地緣政治緊張局勢推動的能源市場飆升,已提高了鐵礦石生產商的成本基礎,特別是通過更高的船用燃料成本和礦場燃料支出的增加。這正開始重塑該行業的成本曲線,進而影響價格動態。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">油價上漲並不直接決定鐵礦石價格,但通過提高邊際生產成本發揮著重要的間接作用。瑞銀估計,原油價格每上漲10美元/桶,可使行業成本增加約0.40至0.80美元/噸,凸顯該板塊對能源市場的敏感性。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-83eb70fe-24dd-3d05-bf50-135e8868453b-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著成本上升,全球成本曲線變得更加陡峭,這意味著在較低價格下,更大比例的供應將變得不經濟。這實際上收緊了供應,並為鐵礦石價格提供了更強的支撐,即使在需求疲軟或庫存高企的時期也是如此。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">瑞銀指出,目前鐵礦石價格已在成本支持位內交易,表明儘管出現中國港口庫存高企和季節性需求疲軟等看跌信號,較高的能源成本仍在幫助支撐價格。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這種影響在不同生產商之間存在差異。瑞銀表示,由於到中國的運輸距離較短,澳洲礦商處於相對有利的位置,而距離更遠或成本更高的生產商則面臨更大的利潤壓力,因為能源成本上升。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">展望未來,瑞銀強調油價走勢將是關鍵驅動因素。能源市場的長期中斷,例如與霍爾木茲海峽周邊緊張局勢相關的中斷,可能進一步推高成本曲線,並為鐵礦石價格提供額外支撐。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">相反,油價若出現任何緩解,將減輕成本壓力,並可能對鐵礦石價格構成壓力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%90%B5%E7%A4%A6%E7%9F%B3%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC%E5%B0%8D%E8%83%BD%E6%BA%90%E6%88%90%E6%9C%AC%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%87%E7%9A%84%E6%95%8F%E6%84%9F%E5%BA%A6%E6%9C%89%E5%A4%9A%E9%AB%98-130025302.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-21 21:27:40",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
